Review this route handler and apply all five questions of the efficacy framework. For each question, state: Pass or Fail, and if Fail, what the specific violation is and what priority it would be assigned.

```typescript
router.post('/workspace/:workspaceId/ai/complete', authMiddleware, requireWorkspace, async (req, res, next) => {
  const { messages, model } = req.body
  const result = await llmRouter.complete({ messages, model })
  await logAuditEvent({ workspaceId: req.workspace!.id, userId: req.user!.id, action: 'ai.complete', payload: { model } })
  res.json({ content: result })
})
